FBIS4-44264 "drweu124__a94022" FBIS-WEU-94-124-A Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 ANNEX Italy & Vatican City Foreign Ministry Welcomes Russia to NATO Program Foreign Ministry Welcomes Russia to NATO Program BR2406075994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1819 GMT 23 Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR2406075994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database English BFN [Unattributed article: "NATO: Italy on Russia in Partnership for Peace"] [Text] (ANSA) Rome, June 23 -- As host to the upcoming G-7 summit in Naples in July, Italy welcomes Russia's entry into the NATO Partnership for Peace program, applauding Russia's growing involvement in international cooperation and the government's efforts at internal reform, according to a statement by the foreign ministry on Thursday [23 June]. The entry of Russia into the Partnership for Peace, the foreign ministry said, "constitutes an important contribution towards the establishment of a European security system based on cooperation and dialogue in a united Europe."
